 *   - gottesman-prl-2012, khabiboulline-prl-2019 — quantum-enhanced telescopy.
 *   - proctor-prl-2018, eldredge-pra-2018 — distributed-estimation theory.
 *   - guo-natphys-2020, xia-prl-2020, malia-nature-2022 — networked demos.
