  description="Sensing applications where the quantum network is load-bearing: entangling sensors at separated nodes to measure a global parameter beyond the standard quantum limit. Networked atomic clocks, quantum-enhanced long-baseline telescopy, and distributed multiparameter estimation — with a reviewed reading list linking to the primary papers."
  references={[
